# Federwiege Python API

Swing2Sleep Smarla API via websocket with signalr protocol.

See tests for example usage.

## Development Setup

- `pip3 install -r requirements_dev.txt`
- `pre-commit install`

## Publishing

- Use flit to publish package to pypi

